				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				  In reference to the Wizard-Magician dispute... Magicians are great for groups, the pets can do a lot of tanking and taunting for the group. Pets also help Magicians solo low blues... BUT, A magician is only as strong as his pet soloing. If the mob kills the pet, they have no way of snaring or rooting the mob, and unless they are SoWed, they usually are killed by mob soon after pet dies... So that 800+ DD spell does no good when a mob is bashing you for 130 points of damage :-)
				</font>
